title: 12-Days of Chicago Christmas Holiday Cards
description:
Sing along to this reimagined classic holiday song, with a Chicago twist! Boxed set includes 12 cards and envelopes. From top to bottom the design features A Picasso in a Pear Tree, Two Lounging Lions, Three Screeching Els, Four Dunking Bulls, Five Frank Lloyd Wrights,  Six Hot Dogs Steaming , Seven Boats a-Sailing, Eight Aldermen Schmoozing, Nine Cubs a-Batting, Ten Pizzas Baking, Eleven Traders Trading, and Twelve Planes a-Landing.

  • Card Dimensions: 5x7 
  • Materials: Boxed set of 12 cards and envelopes
  • Inside Greeting: Season's Greetings
